      <section id="Starting-Section">
        <h3 class="fs-5 header">Starting section</h3>
        <p>Oh look, a new recruit. I'm going to be your instructor today. My name is <b>Myndi</b>, and will do my best to squeeze the best out of you ðŸ˜¤ Nice to meet you!</p>
        <p>To begin with, you need to be wary of the most useful links we have in here.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://www.novaragnarok.com/?module=main">NovaRO Main Site <i class="fa-solid fa-link fa-xs"></i></a> - Useful to check news, your character, the market & spending your well earned real life money.</li>
          <li><a href="https://www.novaragnarok.com/wiki/Main_Page">NovaRO Wikipedia <i class="fa-solid fa-link fa-xs"></i></a> - The all-in-one site for the majority of your questions, thanks to all the contributors.</li>
          <li><a href="https://www.novaragnarok.com/wiki/Leinarth%27s_Rune_Knight_Class_Guide">Leinarth's RK Guide <i class="fa-solid fa-link fa-xs"></i></a> The all-in-one guide for RK <strike>and my competition.</strike> <span class="hover">IT'S JUST A JOKE</span></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.novaragnarok.com/forum/">NovaRO Forum <i class="fa-solid fa-link fa-xs"></i></a> - Perfect to report a bug, write a suggestion or complain, besides that, ignore it.</li>
          <li><a href="https://discord.com/invite/eqHzVK9">NovaRO Discord <i class="fa-solid fa-link fa-xs"></i></a> - If you're here, you probably already know about it.</li>
          <li><a href="https://irowiki.org/wiki/Quests">IronRO Wiki Quest List <i class="fa-solid fa-link fa-xs"></i></a> - This is only useful if you're all about nostalgia and want to do old forgotten quests.</li>
          <li><a href="https://www.divine-pride.net/">Divine Pride <i class="fa-solid fa-link fa-xs"></i></a> - Amazing database. You can check almost anything and most importnatly, future content.</li>
          <li><a href="https://_miel.gitlab.io/ncs/#/">Utility Site <i class="fa-solid fa-link fa-xs"></i></a> - A bit outdated, but still present useful tools for you to use.</li>
          <li><a href="https://zzyx.de/ro/atk">Muh Calculator <i class="fa-solid fa-link fa-xs"></i></a> - Significant calculator both for ATK and MATK. Let's you plan ahead.</li>
          <li><a href="https://ratemyserver.net/">RateMyServer <i class="fa-solid fa-link fa-xs"></i></a> - Honestly, with all the above, useless, but might as well throw it out there.</li>
        </ul>
